<div class="wrapper wrapper_padding clearfix">
	<div class="col-1 about homepage_content">
		<h2>About</h2>
		<hr>
		<p>I'm a software engineer working on my Masters of Computer Science at Johns Hopkins University.</p>
		<p>I'm working on a number of projects, including the benefit streaming platform <a href="http://github.com/nathansforyou">MakeWaves</a> and the social connection app <a href="http://github.com/nathansforyou">Pulse</a>.</p>
		<p>In my free time I love making <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCllD5u2uJcqf54c1MFqdT_A">videos</a>, experimenting with my Vive, and making covers on my SoundCloud.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="col-2 homepage_content">
		<h2>Blog Posts</h2>
		<hr>
		<% @posts.each do |post| %>
			<h3><a href="#"><%= link_to post.title, post %></a></h3>
			<p class="date"><%= post.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d") %></p>
		<% end %>
	</div>
	<div class="col-3 homepage_content">
		<h2>Projects</h2>
		<hr>
		<% @projects.each do |project| %>
			<h3><a href="#"><%= link_to project.title, project %></a></h3>
			<p class="date"><%= project.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d") %></p>
		<% end %>
	</div>
</div>